src/shared/lib/use-carousel-bounds.ts\u0.help:
Don't blindly add missing dependencies. Read the hook callback first.

Bad:
useEffect(() => {
  setCount(count + 1);
}, [count]);

Better:
useEffect(() => {
  setCount((currentCount) => currentCount + 1);
}, []);

If the missing value is recreated every render, move it inside the hook or stabilize it before adding it to deps.

